subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: After winning the singles title in 2003, 2005 and 2007, Serena Williams is back in the semifinals after defeating Svetlana Kuznetsova of Russia, 5-7, 7-5, 6-1.
